Summary: Picture of UFO with few others objects in background
divs: Sighting DetailsI was taken pictures of wind generators in Kaliakra, Bulgaria, during a small vacation with friends. The objects that appear in pictures were not seen in the moment of photographing the wind generators. I observed the objects in the moment that I download the pictures on my computer and start zooming. Please advise your opinion in this subject.
